Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:07.99,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}虽不知能走多远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.04,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}没关系  一个人也能过得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:28.22,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}但其实  没有人是孤独的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:34.39,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}幸福  寂寞  担忧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:43.94,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}都是人生的必由之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.78,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}一小匙的闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.91,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}便能化为一抹微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:57.70,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}或许那是悄悄埋下的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.71,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}让奇迹绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:07.67,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}将那最最重要的宝物找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:13.97,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}便是我们此行的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:20.69,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}虽不知能走多远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:29.24,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}也要用希望编织当下
